body:
Scott: So are you two dating?

Y/N: No, just partners.

Scott: So dating?

Y/N: We work professionally along side each other.

Scott: Hope and I are partners and we’re dating.

Y/N: Doesn’t mean anything Scott.

Scott: (in realization) I got you! Give it a few more weeks.

Y/N: *blushes furiously with annoyance* SCOTT NO!
